{"tid":1358982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7.28 上環之役 （討論）","createTime":"2019-07-24T04:43:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T09:53:26.000Z","uid":263806,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0f7617503a22d68dd709a5658e2722830154b0ab","tid":1358982,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:43:27.000Z","msg":"其實一直都無唔理7.21 上環前線<br />\n<br />\n哩幾日以嚟 唔只連登 我係ig story都見到大家有留意<span style=\"color: red;\">「無預警開槍」「射頭」「催淚彈幾連發」「橋上開槍」「14人入院1人仍危殆」「銀髮族保護」「警方開大燈防影相」</span>好多好多 數之不盡<br />\n<br />\n但大家係咁出post叫人唔好唔記得之外<br />\n又有無討論多啲 7.28上環 嘅方向？<br />\n<br />\n無討論就無發展 無發展就無凝聚<br />\n想問下 <br />\n1）7.28有無入紙申請？定直接踩去？<br />\n2）集合地點？圍堵地點？<br />\n3）預計發展係似 圍警總 定 上水/沙田之役？<br />\n4）...<br />\n<br />\n同埋 再次強烈建議 前線要大家整個tg group<br />\n只for係前線時加人入group<br />\n不作網上加入安排<br />\n哩個group for真係企過前線嘅人討論日後嘅戰略<br />\n唔係for即時戰況討論<br />\n係for日後 for日後<br />\n<br />\n我地前線好寶貴 必須要有一個谷 圍內溝通<br />\n提防有鬼 只接受前線即場加人<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n以下開放討論"},{"pid":"0c160e2dc72e210d07232acce9e3fc2dbea65668","tid":1358982,"uid":74572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:44:49.000Z","msg":"借位 麻煩幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【越洋幫拖】喺美國嘅香港人想收集警暴證據交畀美國警察同議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1358473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1358473</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"73e068a51338db71e19d837fa19ede24d3e532e1","tid":1358982,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6qLY4KX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6qLY4KX.jpg&h=ec4e50e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7db216610eac4d10901f29357a503678b409572e","tid":1358982,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:55:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"